Package org.planit.utils.graph

Interface DirectedVertex

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<Idable>, ExternalIdable, Idable, Serializable, Vertex
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Centroid, Node
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CentroidImpl, DirectedVertexImpl, NodeImpl
    public interface DirectedVertex
extends Vertex
    Directed vertex representation connected to one or more edge segments that have direction. The vertex itself is of course not directional
    Author:
    markr
